snippet.title: Baladins - Official Consoles Announce Trailer | Wholesome Snack December 2023
snippet.description: Dive into the cute fantasy world of Baladins in this latest trailer for the upcoming RPG adventure for 1-4 players. The trailer showcases some of the characters you'll meet and their stories. Baladins will be available on PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, and Nintendo Switch, as well as PC, in early 2024.
